<TEXT>
<P>
The wife of New York Giants linebacker Lawrence Taylor has filed for divorce, 
accusing her husband of extreme cruelty, her attorney said. 
</P>
<P>
Deborah Belinda Taylor filed the papers in Superior Court in Hackensack, N.J., 
attorney Michael K. Diamond said. 
</P>
