COMPOSER ERNEST GOLD WILL RECEIVE AWARD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Composer Ernest Gold will be presented with the sixth annual achievement award 
from the Society for the Preservation of Film Music on Nov. 16 at the Filmland 
Corporate Center in Culver City. 
</P>
<P>
Information: (213) 474-5225. 
</P>
