<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOT TOPICS: HIGH LIFE; 
</P>
<P>
CHOICE SUBJECTS FOR AN OTHERWORLDLY CHAT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Halloween, coming up this Tuesday, is derived from the rites of the Druids 
celebrating the day of Saman, when the Celtic Lord of Death called together the 
souls of the wicked who had died during the past year. 
</P>
<P>
Mediums profess ability to communicate with the souls of the dead -- both 
wicked and good -- at seances. Hot Topics wonders: "If you could talk to 
anybody through a seance, who would you talk to and what would you ask them?" 
</P>
<P>
