(Connelly), Blythe Latimer (Cypress), Monique Verdonck (Loara), Jennifer 
Vineyard (Los Alamitos), Jenny Henderson (Marina), Debbie Maddox (Mater Dei), 
Janet Stouder (Mission Viejo), Nguyen-Hong Hoang (Saddleback), Stacey Kimsey 
