<TEXT>
<P>
University of Florida basketball player Dwayne Schintzius and four former Gator 
athletes -- basketball players Vernon Maxwell, Kenny McClary and Patrick Aaron 
and football player Tommy Duhart -- could be called to testify in a federal 
cocaine trial, a newspaper reported. They are potential government witnesses in 
